{"tid":150143,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人係唔識吞藥","createTime":"2017-03-09T20:27:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-10T06:50:32.000Z","uid":68506,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d1c5465d267d97f9661e47009580815c41fefd23","tid":150143,"uid":68506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T20:27:30.000Z","msg":"今日睇醫生佢開左D抗生素俾我食, 但粒藥鬼死咁大粒(差唔多一節手指尾咁大), 我吞唔到, 無辦法之下唯有啪開一半再吞, 但都係好勉強先吞到, 咁樣會唔會好傷胃(因為佢好似有層衣咁既野包住, 好似係用黎保護粒藥, 等到佢走過左胃之後先至吸收, 可能我知識有限未必啱)<br />\n<br />\n唔知有冇巴打都係同我一樣唔識吞大粒既藥?"},{"pid":"9f8f2761ac128f24143117deb2a38c95ef650cb3","tid":150143,"uid":68506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T20:38:11.000Z","msg":"都唔知點捱落去, 下次食抗生素又要夾硬吞落去, 唔食又會抗藥性病毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cca5fb6fc5688902add8613718e15e3e32749a3","tid":150143,"uid":29717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T20:42:27.000Z","msg":"我都係吞唔到大粒，<br />\n但我覺得含半啖水再放藥落口容易吞啲"},{"pid":"9b166da3467e20653794b5fc6dc1278f306e91a7","tid":150143,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T20:42:37.000Z","msg":"含住粒藥，含淡水之後連藥帶水吞落肚，點會吞唔到，除非粒藥大過你食道口啫"},{"pid":"9281246ab461fdd07d6bc478bfc89ea627e29879","tid":150143,"uid":12448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T20:50:35.000Z","msg":"我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n吞到一半卡住 嘔返出嚟<br />\n多多粒都唔夠我嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n見到啲朋友連水都唔洗飲就吞到好羨慕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3adb8b021d580930b07e124e9d9ed1f9d6230ddf","tid":150143,"uid":72638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T20:53:55.000Z","msg":"啪開藥一半分兩次食<br />\n會易吞D"},{"pid":"ac9922bcc4909bc158b78d12c1b253d08b579ac2","tid":150143,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T21:13:38.000Z","msg":"水都唔洗飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過平時怕傷喉都會飲<br />\n<br />\n利申食咗半年抗生素"},{"pid":"0f217dfbbf5c19df539b33573c417c63dfb279f2","tid":150143,"uid":611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T21:42:28.000Z","msg":"一樣 要好細粒先吞到<br />\n大粒啲要必開幾份<br />\n有時太大粒會卡撚左係喉 嘔返出黎<br />\n睇醫生食晒一Set藥要飲佢杯幾兩杯食 飽到暈"},{"pid":"62b1136c99a498d2e3380e7244b036fea06fa305","tid":150143,"uid":2373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T21:52:04.000Z","msg":"渣ga"},{"pid":"e0a027e4058987fa340dbf202e5fe9166d2c133a","tid":150143,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T22:13:23.000Z","msg":"有時粒藥痴住喺上顎沖唔到落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nlam番出嚟粒藥已經溶溶地，好苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ffbcd06ff31752acf85e4b0d8e6266b35e53ed5","tid":150143,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T22:19:33.000Z","msg":"當粒藥唔存在 好似平時飲水咁吞水就吞到藥丸㗎喇"},{"pid":"276aa1bc487820e7750588e2161d610820960e60","tid":150143,"uid":44160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T22:22:53.000Z","msg":"粒藥放利底，加啖水吞，幾大粒都冇問題"},{"pid":"68be7f5dd08b0b8aa5b01ca701aa448bd856e8b5","tid":150143,"uid":10845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T22:41:59.000Z","msg":"吞唔到係因為你驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 慢慢練下就得<br />\n細細個一吞唔到就罵到仆街<br />\n到依家已經練成一次過吞一堆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40821dd653132966bedc3d1243d0b66c6bafdf64","tid":150143,"uid":20448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T23:29:21.000Z","msg":"吞唔到咪係屎忽窿塞返上去囉 仲要問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\